data.description: 4.59 acre lot home nestled in the charming Northside community, this home has 4-bedrooms, 2-bathrooms and additional office/study. Open-concept. The cozy living room features a 15ft vaulted natural wood ceiling with beautiful stained concrete floors. Plantation shutters, custom barn doors and granite countertops for added charm. Outside you will find this property would make a perfect place for a Horse Farm.This home is situated in a family-friendly neighborhood with excellent schools and easy access to Northside's amenities. Owner states VA loan is assumable.
